snippet.title: Warframe | Heart of Deimos Teaser
snippet.description:
The beating heart of Deimos grows louder. 

Catch the reveal of our next update, Heart of Deimos, during TennoLive on August 1 at 5 p.m. ET and get Hydroid Prime free! Learn more: http://wrfr.me/hod
